reviewText: mmmmm some good some bad some very bad lol but worth the price
it was good for the price
8 wonderful movies. I really enjoyed them all and so will you
Not even one movie in this collection (and i use the word collection with great hesitation) I would give 2 stars to.
Some of the movies are very good, some are ok and a couple are bombs, but it is less than $5!  You can not go wrong on a deal like this.
